features: [Quantity And Size]: You will receive 16pcs WB2K101 rubber feet for your replacement needs.1 mm vent hole, 4.5 mm/0.18 inch shaft diameter and 5.5 mm/0.22 inch shaft length, for 3/16 inch hole.

[Function]: Range grate rubber feet secure to the bottom of the burner grates, preventing the cooktop from being scratched, keeping the grates level, providing even cooking, and preventing cookware from tipping over due to unstable grate placement.

[High Quality]: Our WB2K101 range burner grate rubber feet are made of high quality, abrasion and heat resistant rubber material. Excellent heat resistance, not easy to melt and emit pungent odor due to high temperature.

[Easy Installation]: No tools are needed, just flip the grate over, then take out the old rubber feet and finally put the replacement parts in, it is recommended to apply glue or heating grade silicone on the rubber feet to ensure a better fit.
[Fits For]: WB2K101 rubber foot replacements fit for GE, Kenmore, Hotpoint stoves, replacement part numbers WB02K0101, 247410, PS241358, EAP241358, PS2353327, AP2622260, AP4411611 and more.

reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Foot insert too small
reviews.reviewText: The product advertises that this is a fit for the WB02T10461 burner grate. Upon arrival, the diameter of the foot insert is too narrow for the grate. This has been a common problem for several companies listed on Amazon.There is a work around, however. You can use a bead of silicone around the foot to help adhere the foot to the grate. This is a semi-permanent solution but better than nothing.
